Package: NSmetabolism
Title: N-Station Stream Metabolism Modelling
Version: 0.6.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Talluto",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mtalluto@gmail.com")
Description: Implements a stream metabolism model for estimating gross primary productivity and ecosystem respiration. The model extends common 1- and 2-station models to n stations, with the potential for latent (unobserved) stations.
